'''Mohannad Mahmoud Saleh Abu Taha''' ({{langx|ar|مُهَنَّد مَحْمُود صَالِح أَبُو طٰهٰ}}; born 2 February 2003) is a Jordanian [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)#Winger|winger]] or [[left-back]] for [[Iraq Stars League]] club [[Al-Quwa Al-Jawiya]], and the [[Jordan national football team|Jordan national team]].

==Club career==
=== Al-Wehdat ===
Born in [[Amman]], Abu Taha is a youth product of [[Al-Wehdat SC|Al-Wehdat]]. He was promoted to the first team in 2021 at the age of 18.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://akhbarhayat.com/870791/%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87-%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%B4%D8%AD-%D9%84%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%B6%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%88%D9%85-%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B1/|title=أبو طه مرشح للانضمام إلى دوري نجوم قطر|date=20 June 2023 |publisher=Akhbarhayat|access-date=1 February 2024|language=ar}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://alghad.com/Section-180/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%88%D8%A5%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8A-%D9%84%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87-1352394|title=عرضان قطري وإماراتي لنجم الوحدات أبو طه|publisher=Alghad|access-date=1 February 2024|language=ar}}</ref>

In January 2023, Abu Taha nearly joined the reserves team of [[Belgian Pro League]] side [[KAA Gent|Gent]] on a 6-month loan deal with option to buy, but the deal was not completed because the transfer window closed before the player registered.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://royanews.tv/news/293414|title=الوحدات يعلن احتراف مهند أبو طه في الدوري البلجيكي|publisher=Royal News|access-date=1 February 2024|language=ar}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.addustour.com/articles/1328124-%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87-%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%82%D8%B9-%D9%84%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%BA%D9%8A%D9%86%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%84%D8%AC%D9%8A%D9%83%D9%8A%C2%A0|title=ابو طه يوقع لنادي ريال غينت البلجيكي |publisher=Addustour|access-date=1 February 2024|language=ar}}</ref>

He had played an important role in the [[2023–24 Jordan FA Cup]], where he had scored one of the goals in the final against [[Al-Hussein SC (Irbid)|Al-Hussein]].<ref>{{cite web |title=نجم منتخب الأردن يحترف بدوري نجوم العراق.. من هو "مهند أبو طه"؟ |url=https://www.alsumaria.tv/Entertainment-News/500955/sports/%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%AA%D8%B1%D9%81-%D8%A8%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82-%D9%85%D9%86-%D9%87%D9%88-%D9%85%D9%87%D9%86%D8%AF-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87%D8%9F |website=alsumaria.tv |publisher=Al-Sumaria |access-date=26 September 2024 |language=Arabic |date=24 September 2024}}</ref> He was noted for having played at a variety of wing and central positions while at Al-Wehdat.

With his contract running out towards the end of the [[2023–24 Jordanian Pro League|2023–24 season]], Abu Taha had refused a contract extension from Al-Wehdat, as he desired to play professionally abroad.<ref>{{cite web |title=نجم منتخب الأردن يحترف بدوري نجوم العراق.. من هو "مهند أبو طه"؟ |url=https://www.alsumaria.tv/Entertainment-News/500955/sports/%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%AA%D8%B1%D9%81-%D8%A8%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82-%D9%85%D9%86-%D9%87%D9%88-%D9%85%D9%87%D9%86%D8%AF-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87%D8%9F |website=alsumaria.tv |publisher=Al-Sumaria |access-date=26 September 2024 |language=Arabic |date=24 September 2024}}</ref>

=== Al-Karkh ===
On 14 August 2024, Abu Taha was linked to join [[Iraq Stars League]] club [[Al-Karkh SC|Al-Karkh]],<ref>{{cite web |title=الدولي مهند ابو طه في طريقه الى الكرخ العراقي.. والنجف يقترب من رجائي عايد |url=https://jo24.net/article/509071 |website=jo24.net |publisher=jo24 |access-date=14 September 2024 |language=Arabic |date=14 August 2024}}</ref> which on 23 September 2024, he signed a deal to join the club for an undisclosed deal,<ref>{{cite web |title=مهند أبو طه يوقع للكرخ العراقي |url=https://m.kooora.com/?n=1356775&o=n&cz=1958&pg=7 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=26 September 2024 |language=Arabic |date=23 September 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=أبو طه ينضم للكرخ العراقي |url=https://www.mala3eb.com/Section_113/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86%D9%8A/%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87-%D9%8A%D9%86%D8%B6%D9%85-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%AE-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%8A_200609 |website=mala3eb.com |publisher=Mala3eb |access-date=26 September 2024 |language=Arabic |date=23 September 2024}}</ref> as well as a one-year contract.<ref>{{cite web |title=نجم منتخب الأردن يحترف بدوري نجوم العراق.. من هو "مهند أبو طه"؟ |url=https://www.alsumaria.tv/Entertainment-News/500955/sports/%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%AA%D8%B1%D9%81-%D8%A8%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82-%D9%85%D9%86-%D9%87%D9%88-%D9%85%D9%87%D9%86%D8%AF-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87%D8%9F |website=alsumaria.tv |publisher=Al-Sumaria |access-date=26 September 2024 |language=Arabic |date=24 September 2024}}</ref>

=== Al-Orobah ===
On 31 January 2025, Abu Taha joined [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al-Orobah FC|Al-Orobah]] on a six-month loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=العروبة يستعير أبو طه من الكرخ |url=https://arriyadiyah.com/859263}}</ref> By going on loan, he agreed with his parent club to sign a contract extension for an additional season.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hassan |first1=Fayez |title=أين سيلعب مهند أبو طه وبكر كلبونة الموسم المقبل؟ |url=https://www.winwin.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A3%D9%8A%D9%86-%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D9%85%D9%87%D9%86%D8%AF-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%B7%D9%87-%D9%88%D8%A8%D9%83%D8%B1-%D9%83%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%88%D9%86%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%88%D8%B3%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%82%D8%A8%D9%84%D8%9F |website=winwin.com |publisher=WinWin |access-date=26 July 2025 |language=Arabic |date=2 July 2025}}</ref>

===Al-Quwa Al-Jawiya===
On 10 August 2025, Abu Taha joined [[Al-Quwa Al-Jawiya]] from [[Al-Karkh SC|Al-Karkh]].<ref>{{cite web |title=القوة الجوية يتعاقد مع الأردني مهند أبو طه |url=https://ina.iq/ar/sport/240631-.html |website=ina.iq |publisher=Iraqi News Agency |access-date=10 August 2025 |language=Arabic |date=10 August 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
On 17 October 2023, Abu Taha made his international debut with the [[Jordan national football team|Jordan national team]] against [[Iraq national football team|Iraq]] as part of the [[2023 Jordan International Tournament]] third place match.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2023/10/17/world/friendlies/iraq/jordan/4262349/|title=Iraq vs. Jordan 2 - 2|publisher=Soccerway|access-date=1 February 2024}}</ref>

In January 2024, Abu Taha was included in Jordan's 26-men squad for the [[2023 AFC Asian Cup]].<ref>{{cite news|title=قائمة النشامى لنهائيات كأس آسيا 🇯🇴|trans-title=Al-Nashama list for the Asian Cup Finals 🇯🇴|url=https://twitter.com/JordanFA/status/1741356148530299195|publisher=Jordan Football Association|website=Twitter|date=31 December 2023|access-date=1 February 2024|language=ar}}</ref>

